$ Oracle: Init parameter OPTIMIZER_ADAPTIVE_PLANS
@ optimizer_adaptive_plans

`optimizer_adaptive_plans` controls all types of → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/execution/plan/adaptive[adaptive plans].
-
Setting it to `false` disables the following adaptive features:
  • nested loop join/hash join selection
  • star tranformation bitmap pruning
  • adaptive parallel distribution method

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
